    <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">A rectangular pillbox with an enclosed square plan section for three Light Machine Guns and an adjacent open area housing a mounting for a Light Anti Aircraft weapon. Designed by DFW branch 3.</skos:scopeNote>
