    <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="en">Watch Office (343/43)</skos:prefLabel>
    <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">A modification of WATCH OFFICE (12779/41) where the original large windows were removed and smaller frames fitted, the gap being filled with straight-joint brickwork.</skos:scopeNote>
